with this annoying jerk again.

05:19.920 --> 05:21.186
Ugh.

05:21.188 --> 05:23.789
- She'll come around.
Give her some space.

05:23.791 --> 05:25.724
Shahzad, I'm proud of you.

05:25.860 --> 05:28.193
I can't wait
to hear your speech.

05:28.195 --> 05:29.528
- Oh, man.

