for 15 years

05:52.820 --> 05:54.287
so you wouldn't have to.

05:54.421 --> 05:55.754
Go ahead, over there.
Go ahead. Do something.

05:55.890 --> 05:59.492
- "That's okay,
because all I have to be

05:59.626 --> 06:04.096
"is the one and only...

06:04.231 --> 06:06.031
original me."

06:06.033 --> 06:08.367
[cheers and applause]

06:08.503 --> 06:09.702
- Read it again.

06:09.837 --> 06:11.904
- What's up, O.G.?

06:12.039 --> 06:13.572
Mind if I read to the kids?

06:13.574 --> 06:15.875
- Sure, youngblood.

06:19.180 --> 06:21.314
- "I'm not fast
like a cheetah..."

06:21.448 --> 06:23.983
<i> [dramatic hip-hop music]</i>

06:23.985 --> 06:25.650
- You should count 'em.

06:25.652 --> 06:28.053
- What's your name?
- Daveon.

06:28.055 --> 06:31.456
- Daveon, I'ma tell you like
I told your motherfuckin' boss.

06:31.592 --> 06:35.661
Tompkins-Marcy Community Center
is off-limits.

06:35.663 --> 06:37.262
- Is everything all right,
Mr. Tray?

06:37.264 --> 06:39.064
- Everything is all right,
Emmitt.

06:39.066 --> 06:41.734
You just in time to walk
my friend out the door.

06:41.869 --> 06:44.337
- Oh, it's like that, O.G.?
- It's like that.

06:44.471 --> 06:46.005
- Your funeral.

06:46.140 --> 06:48.741
