nigga.

06:51.478 --> 06:56.682
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

06:56.684 --> 06:58.351
- Tell me what the fuck
is going on,

06:58.485 --> 07:00.152
and do not bullshit me.

07:03.090 --> 07:04.089
- After we went
before the board

07:04.225 --> 07:05.490
to get the center reopened,

07:05.626 --> 07:07.092
