we was gonna lose the vote,

07:07.228 --> 07:09.294
so I bribed
one of the commissioners.

07:09.296 --> 07:12.231
- And I'm guessing you didn't
take out a bank loan.

07:12.233 --> 07:13.966
- No.

07:14.101 --> 07:15.368
But the guy that gave me
the money,

07:15.502 --> 07:17.570
I thought was legit,
and that's word is bond.

07:17.705 --> 07:21.840
- We wouldn't be here
if the man was legit.

07:21.976 --> 07:23.776
- Veesy, you tell me
what the fuck

07:23.911 --> 07:25.444
I was supposed to do,
nothing?

07:25.580 --> 07:26.912
If I'd have did that,
we wouldn't have

07:27.048 --> 07:29.282
no community center at all.

07:32.187 --> 07:36.121
- Tray,
if we didn't get that vote,

07:36.123 --> 07:39.524
we would've just
figured it out,

07:39.526 --> 07:42.061
done something else.

07:42.196 --> 07:44.797
What hurts me is that
you just went on ahead

07:44.932 --> 07:46.365
and did it behind my back.

07:48.335 --> 07:50.203
- I know you tired
of hearing this.

07:50.337 --> 07:53.205
I'm sorry, a'ight?
I'm sorry.

07:53.340 --> 07:55.007
Give me one more chance
to make this right.

07:55.142 --> 07:56.541
I know I could.

07:56.677 --> 07:58.343
- How?

07:58.345 --> 08:01.480
How could you possibly
make this better?

08:01.482 --> 08:02.547
How big is this, really?

08:02.549 --> 08:05.550
What else are you
not telling me?

08:05.552 --> 08:07.420
I don't even trust you.

08:07.554 --> 08:09.955
And I don't work with people
that I do not trust.

08:09.957 --> 08:13.292
So pack up your shit and leave.

08:13.294 --> 08:15.227
Dead ass, you're fired.

08:15.362 --> 08:17.830
Matter of fact,
give me your security badge.

08:17.965 --> 08:19.799
Leave the keys at security.

08:21.636 --> 08:23.369
Come on.

08:25.240 --> 08:28.707
Everything we been through,

08:28.709 --> 08:30.976
you haven't learned nothing.

08:30.978 --> 08:38.117
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

08:40.321 --> 08:42.321
- What is a maverick exactly?

08:42.457 --> 08:44.389
