with a joke?

08:55.002 --> 08:56.669
- His being picked is the joke.

08:56.804 --> 08:59.071
- You guys, you have
to help me fix this.

08:59.206 --> 09:01.206
- Oh, I would help,
but I'm too basic.

09:01.342 --> 09:02.375
Remember?

09:03.744 --> 09:05.945
- Cool.
Cool, cool.

09:06.080 --> 09:07.813
