09:09.284 --> 09:10.749
in the auditorium,
I could pull a fire alarm.

09:10.885 --> 09:11.884
- Not helping.

09:12.019 --> 09:16.889
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

09:17.024 --> 09:18.090
[car horn beeps]

09:18.225 --> 09:19.892
- Tray!
Our ride is here!

09:20.027 --> 09:21.360
- Ma.
- Hey.

09:21.362 --> 09:22.895
- You seen the gifts
I got the kids?

09:23.030 --> 09:24.697
- No, I haven't, but you could
give them the gifts later.

09:24.832 --> 09:26.165
Come on, we gotta go.

09:26.167 --> 09:27.500
- I need to give 'em
to 'em now, Ma.

09:27.634 --> 09:28.901
