09:30.437 --> 09:31.837
the community center
on our way there.

09:31.839 --> 09:33.172
- You go ahead.
I don't want you to be late.

09:33.308 --> 09:34.840
I'll meet you
at the graduation.

09:34.842 --> 09:36.909
- What's going on?
Uh-uh.

09:37.044 --> 09:38.311
