a little strange now.

09:38.445 --> 09:39.979
- I'm not acting strange, Ma.

09:40.114 --> 09:41.446
I just want everything
to be perfect, okay?

09:41.448 --> 09:43.316
Amira and Shahzad,
they deserve this.

09:43.450 --> 09:45.584
- Well, graduation is not just
for the kids.

09:45.586 --> 09:47.186
It's for the parents too.

09:47.322 --> 09:49.654
