and let us enjoy this day.

09:49.656 --> 09:51.324
- Ma, can I be honest with you?
- What?

09:51.458 --> 09:52.925
- I just feel bad that I never

09:53.060 --> 09:54.459
got to give you
a day like this.

09:54.595 --> 09:55.728
That's all.

09:55.863 --> 09:57.663
- Okay. Stop.

09:57.798 --> 09:59.198
Now...
[chuckles]

09:59.200 --> 10:02.535
I gotta admit that I used
to be angry about it.

10:02.670 --> 10:06.205
But look at my baby now.
You got your life on track.

10:06.341 --> 10:08.874
You got a good job
at the community center.

10:08.876 --> 10:11.877
You're finally the man
I always knew you could be.

10:11.879 --> 10:13.746
Come here!

10:13.881 --> 10:16.615
Oh, God, my baby.

10:16.617 --> 10:18.351
All right,
I'ma save you a seat.

10:18.485 --> 10:20.085
- All right.
