10:20.087 --> 10:21.286
- All right, Ma. All right.
- Okay?

10:21.422 --> 10:23.422
- Our whole class
is gonna remember me

10:23.558 --> 10:26.492
as the dumbass
with the boring speech.

10:27.628 --> 10:28.761
- Shahzad,
I've never told you this,

10:28.896 --> 10:30.429
but I really admire the way

10:30.431 --> 10:32.231
you're willing to let people
think you're weird.

10:32.233 --> 10:33.432
- I don't know
if that's supposed

10:33.434 --> 10:35.500
to make me feel better
or worse.

10:35.502 --> 10:37.703
- You're an original.
Own it.

10:37.705 --> 10:39.572
Lean into your strengths
with that speech.

10:39.707 --> 10:41.840
Don't try to impress people
or sound smart.

10:41.976 --> 10:43.308
Just be you.
- [laughs]

10:43.444 --> 10:45.510
Okay, now I'm sure
you're complimenting me

10:45.646 --> 10:47.112
by insulting me.

10:47.114 --> 10:49.248
- I am.
And I'm never gonna stop.

10:49.250 --> 10:51.417
[both laugh]

10:55.189 --> 10:57.390
- Man, I can't believe
I lost my keys.

10:57.524 --> 10:58.991
- You just called me
after my workout.

10:59.126 --> 11:01.193
I gotta run home and change.
- Yeah.

11:01.328 --> 11:03.429
- See you at graduation.
- Yeah.

11:11.672 --> 11:13.138
- Yo.

11:13.140 --> 11:16.541
You said ain't nobody afraid
of no nigga named Percy, huh?

11:16.677 --> 11:18.611
How 'bout a nigga named Poison?

11:18.746 --> 11:21.747
- What, you gonna shoot me?
That's your plan?

11:21.749 --> 11:23.416
Think I'm afraid of you?

11:23.550 --> 11:25.550
Poison, you think
I'm scared to die?

11:25.552 --> 11:26.685
- Nigga.

11:26.687 --> 11:27.953
